    • Field Detail

      • satellites

        private java.util.TreeMap<java.lang.String,​SatelliteDescription> satellites
        Descriptions of satellites indexed by satellite id. The descriptions are obtained from the SSC scansat software. The descriptions are periodically retrieved and stored in this map.
